name: Commons and Cove
description:
This week we'll take Tulip Street to the Dartmouth Common, do a lap of the baseball field, and then head towards the Dartmouth Cove trail. We will make our way back via Newcastle, Albert, and Hawthorne. Once we get to the pond there will be an optional lap to bring us to 6km or you can call it at 5km!
As always, we meet at the Sullivans Pond Gazebo at 6:30pm.
